&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;pleasant&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The given word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Horrendous&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;very bad or unpleasant&lt;/strong&gt;. (बहुत बुरा या अप्रिय)

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;horrendous&lt;/strong&gt; pain stopped and it was all over&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;​Let&amp;#39;s see the&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;meaning&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;of other given options:-
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Frightening&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;means&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;making you feel afraid or shocked&lt;/strong&gt;. (डराने या सदमा पहुँचाने वाला)
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;His face under the moonlight was &lt;strong&gt;frightening&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Dreary&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;not at all interesting or attractive; boring&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(नीरस या अनाकर्षक; उबाऊ)
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;Life has become so &lt;strong&gt;dreary&lt;/strong&gt; and exhausting&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Watchful&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;means &lt;strong&gt;being&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;careful to notice things&lt;/strong&gt;. (जागरूक, सतर्क)
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;His mother kept a &lt;strong&gt;watchful&lt;/strong&gt; eye on him&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Pleasant&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;nice, enjoyable, or friendly&lt;/strong&gt;. (सुहाना, आनंददायक या अनुकूल)
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;Our room is &lt;strong&gt;pleasant&lt;/strong&gt; and comfortable&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
			&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 4&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;antonyms&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;of the word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Horrendous&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; are&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;pleasant&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;, nice,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;alluring&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;synonyms&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;of the word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Horrendous&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; are&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;frightening, horrible, disgusting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;Flamboyant&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;#39;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ostentatious &lt;/strong&gt;refers to a display that is showy, pretentious, or designed to impress. It is often characterized by an unnecessary display of wealth or elegance. (दिखावटी, प्रदर्शनपूर्ण, या प्रभावित करने के लिए डिज़ाइन किया गया। इसमें अक्सर धन या भव्यता का अनावश्यक प्रदर्शन होता है।)

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example Sentence&lt;/strong&gt; for Ostentatious: Her ostentatious lifestyle was a matter of gossip in their small town.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flamboyant&lt;/strong&gt; means strikingly bold or showy, often associated with confidence, style and an inclination to attract attention. (बेहद बहादुर या दिखावटी, जिससे आत्मविश्वास, शैली और ध्यान आकर्षित करने की प्रवृत्ति जुड़ी है।)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example Sentence&lt;/strong&gt; for Flamboyant: His flamboyant dressing sense always made him stand out in a crowd.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Therefore, the correct answer is&lt;strong&gt; Option 1.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Subdued&lt;/strong&gt;: (used about a person) quieter and with less energy than usual. ((व्&amp;zwj;यक्ति) अभिभूत; शांत तथा सामान्&amp;zwj;य से कम ऊर्जा सहित।)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Restrained&lt;/strong&gt;: Characterized by reserve or moderation; unemotional or dispassionate. (शांत, भावहीन।)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Appropriate&lt;/strong&gt;: Suitable or proper in the circumstances. (&lt;strong&gt;परिस्थितियों में उपयुक्त या उचित।)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&lt;strong&gt; &amp;#39;Option 4&amp;#39; &lt;/strong&gt;i.e.&lt;strong&gt; &amp;#39;Crypt&amp;#39;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;The word&lt;strong&gt; &amp;quot;crypt&amp;quot; &lt;/strong&gt;is the closest &lt;strong&gt;synonym&lt;/strong&gt; to &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;vault&amp;quot; &lt;/strong&gt;in this context.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A vault&lt;/strong&gt; can refer to a secure room or compartment, often made of steel or reinforced concrete, used for the safekeeping of valuables, such as money, documents, or precious items.(&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;तिजोरी)&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A crypt&lt;/strong&gt; is an underground room or vault beneath a church that is used as a chapel or burial place.(&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;गुप्त कक्ष)&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Therefore, the&lt;strong&gt; correct answer&lt;/strong&gt; is:&lt;strong&gt; &amp;#39;Crypt&amp;#39;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

