&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Raisins:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;dried grapes.(&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;किशमिश)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ration:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;a fixed amount of a commodity officially allowed to each person during a time of shortage or scarcity.(&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;राशन)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Monarch:&lt;/strong&gt; a sovereign head of state, typically a king, queen, or emperor.(&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;महाराजा)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
